{
  "id": "adv_event_2205_01_02",
  "title": "心紡ぎ合う輝きの競演 2話 今のままじゃダメ",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2205_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2205_01_02-ski001.m4a",
      "text": "それじゃあ、今日から改めてよろしくね、千紗",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well then‚ let's start fresh from today‚ Chisa.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2205_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2205_01_02-chs001.m4a",
      "text": "う、うん。こちらこそ……よろしく、お姉ちゃん",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Y-Yeah. I'm looking forward with it… ‚ Onee-chan.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 4.8666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "大会に向けて練習スケジュールを組んだの",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I've made a practice schedule for the tournament.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 10.2333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2205_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2205_01_02-ski002.m4a",
      "text": "いつもと勝手が違うから、あくまで仮だけどね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Since it's different from our usual routine‚ it's just a temporary plan.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 14.5,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_paper-01.m4a",
          "delay": 0
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2205_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2205_01_02-chs002.m4a",
      "text": "わ……お姉ちゃん、さすが……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Wow… Onee-chan‚ you're amazing…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 18.9666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "千紗も意見があればどんどん言って",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If you have any opinions‚ Chisa‚ feel free to speak up.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 22.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2205_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2205_01_02-ski003.m4a",
      "text": "いつでも調整するから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We can always make adjustments.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 25.0666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2205_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2205_01_02-chs003.m4a",
      "text": "う、うん、分かった……！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Y-Yeah‚ got it…!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 27.5333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "1、2、3、4！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "1‚ 2‚ 3‚ 4!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 35.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2205_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2205_01_02-ski004.m4a",
      "text": "千紗、大丈夫？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Chisa‚ are you okay?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 38.41,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2205_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2205_01_02-chs004.m4a",
      "text": "うん……大丈夫、だよ……っ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah… I'm fine…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 41.0666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "（次のステップは……私が一歩引いたら）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(Next step… If I take a step back…)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 46.4666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2205_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2205_01_02-ski005.m4a",
      "text": "（千紗が目立てるかな）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(Will Chisa stand out?)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 49.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "（ここで……私が一歩引けば）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(If I take a step back here…)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 52,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2205_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2205_01_02-chs005.m4a",
      "text": "（お姉ちゃんが引き立つかも……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(Onee-chan might shine…)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 55.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "一同",
      "speakerNameEn": "Everyone",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2205_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2205_01_02-chs006.m4a",
      "text": "（せーの……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(Ready‚ set…)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 57.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "一同",
      "speakerNameEn": "Everyone",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2205_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2205_01_02-chs007.m4a",
      "text": "……あっ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Ah!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 60,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2205_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2205_01_02-ski008.m4a",
      "text": "ご、ごめんね？　二人とも下がっちゃったね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "S-Sorry? We both stepped back‚ huh?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 61.4666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2205_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2205_01_02-chs008.m4a",
      "text": "あはは、そうだね……私こそ、ごめんね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ahaha‚ yeah… I'm sorry too.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 66.2333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "（あ、あれ……？　また二人とも譲っちゃった……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(Huh…? We both yielded again…)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 73.2333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2205_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2205_01_02-chs009.m4a",
      "text": "（これじゃ、二人とも目立たなくなっちゃう）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(We might end up not standing out at all…)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 78.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "千紗、ちょっと休憩にしましょう？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Chisa‚ let's take a break‚ okay?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 82.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2205_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2205_01_02-ski009.m4a",
      "text": "話し合いもしたいし",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I also want to have a discussion.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 85.9333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2205_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2205_01_02-chs010.m4a",
      "text": "そ、そうだね……私も、話したかった",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Y-Yeah‚ that sounds good… I wanted to talk too.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 88.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "なんだかうまくいかないわね……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Things don't seem to go well…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 94.4478729248,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2205_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2205_01_02-ski010.m4a",
      "text": "グループで練習してる時と感覚が違うというか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The feeling is different from when we practice as a group.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 97.6812062581,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "う、うん……お姉ちゃんとなら",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Y-Yeah… I thought we could do well",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 102.0145395915,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2205_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2205_01_02-chs011.m4a",
      "text": "最初からうまく出来ると思ったんだけど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "from the beginning if it's with Onee-chan…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 105.4912062581,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "サニピと月ストで練習している時と",
      "translations": {
        "en": "When we practice with Sunny Peace and Moon Tempest…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 109.0478729248,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2205_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2205_01_02-ski011.m4a",
      "text": "何が違うのかしら……？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What's different‚ I wonder…?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 111.8145395915,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2205_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2205_01_02-chs012.m4a",
      "text": "違い、かぁ……うーん……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The difference‚ huh… Hmm…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 114.2145395915,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2205_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2205_01_02-ski012.m4a",
      "text": "五人グループの時と、二人組ユニットの時……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "In a five-person group‚ and in a duo team…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 119.0812062581,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "……そういえば、サニピでは……いつも怜ちゃんが",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Now that you mention it‚ in Sunny Peace…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 123.6478729248,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2205_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2205_01_02-chs013.m4a",
      "text": "どんどん引っ張ってくれてる……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Rei-chan always takes the lead…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 127.4478729248,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "確かにそうね。それで言うと……月ストでは",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That's true. Speaking of Moon Tempest…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 130.2812062581,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2205_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2205_01_02-ski013.m4a",
      "text": "琴乃ちゃんが怜ちゃんみたいに引っ張ってくれてるかな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Kotono-chan leads like Rei-chan‚ I guess.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 134.4478729248,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
